rc=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n越係遠離中間虛線嘅政治目標，係代表要削弱敵對政權/組織越多，或者佢嘅武裝力量/人民傷戰後仲留低幾多<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">雖然話係要消滅敵對政權，但呢度係指政治上嘅消滅</span></strong>。政權更替，或者正接講更換林鄭政府呢個行動本身係唔一定要流血嘅<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>但當政權選擇左用戰爭黎回應你想佢下台呢個要求，咁就註定左佢起碼會放你血先</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPnNJbz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPnNJbz.png&h=2dcbacde&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:26:56.000Z","msg":"雖然應該都無人會睇，但我補返個source先<br />\n不過呢張圖都係出現得分幾鐘亦都無好詳細講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nClausewitz and Jomini: Their Interaction<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pRw2KuEXRI0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpRw2KuEXRI0&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAw08L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=87a87581\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pRw2KuEXRI0</a>"},{"pid":"c4146754702a8aad7f70033e1ee9e2587fc03b34","tid":1596946,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"估唔到琴晚咁夜都仲有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕力一推下先"},{"pid":"e1e94a9e020a21a93348c52a51ca0c42a6beea01","tid":1596946,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d34dd64415d14a39d862930cd7285bcaf89aee46","tid":1596946,"uid":235465,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"今日都有個日本教授講過 現階段以示威黎講 無論暴力定非暴力 都幾乎無可能達到真普選<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隨左靠美帝就認真無咩方法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:48:25.000Z","msg":"個日本教授講野係邊度睇得返？<br />\n我覺得又無佢咁悲觀嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講其他，最起碼唔係香港人咁主動為美國帶路，佢地都唔方便直接介入"},{"pid":"ba406f8e5c778e328bd72b2664766f9c2ee15284","tid":1596946,"uid":202720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27